# Filter the forest
forest <- nepal %>%
  filter(Category == "Forest")
#forest <- st_transform(forest, crs = 3857)
forest = forest[1:50, ]
# Plot the data
ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = forest, fill = "green", color = "darkgreen") +
  labs(title = "Forest Areas in Nepal") +
  theme_minimal()

a = aggregate(fapar_ds, by = forest, FUN = min)
